Text.Value: Strange warriors... gold skin... silver blades...
*You realise the tiefling's body has been torn open by huge hands.*
Where did you see those warriors?
Anything of value you happen to have?
Quick of foot, this one, to avoid githyanki hunters.
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: The corpse collapses, never again to speak

Text.Value: What brought you to the village?
*The tiefling's corpse stirs with the spell.*
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: The corpse collapses, never again to speak

Text.Value: You saw githyanki. Where were they?

Synopsis: The player can cast Speak with Dead on a tiefling the ogres tore open to feed on.
